column5: When you spend 15 minutes in a bathroom stall at work, watching bass fishing videos on your smart phone!!   Or in my case (because I detest bass fishing) watching Mike's new Promo Musky video!
That was deep
You actually look into your rearview mirror to make sure no one is following you to your secret fishing spot.
You call your kid 'smallmouth', because even when he smiles widely his lips still don't reach past his eyes.
Every fish you've caught has been dragged in a livewell to 15 min from where you caught it, to take a picture
Your shirt costs more than your rod. HH
You fish pike opener in a lake with nothing but largemouth...   I saw this last year, 3 guys, rigged out Ranger, etc etc.    Talk about sportsman, lol.
Your boat costs more than your house.
You can't catch fish with teeth!
Save everything else, eat a bass...  Can't wait for the first stringer full of summer smallies!
You laugh at the musky guys daily ...
...you refer to the 4 major food groups as worms, crawdads, grubs, and spinnerbaits.
When jerk, jerk, pause technique is used outside of fishing..........
you keep a fishing rod in the any vehicle you're driving in, "just in case"...
You drive your $70,000 bass bote through boulder fields and raging white water to get to the basses!!!!  http://www.bassmaster.com/video/scary-moment-rough-water

for the young guys.....  you say shes about a 6lb smallie  you say Shes no keeper but id catch and release it for the trill of it  "I look at fishing how i look at "young" relationships, if she leaves dont waste your time trying to catch it, get your rod back out there and get a bigger one" - Alex Mazzuca
You lip you're newborn to kiss him goodnight!
You refer to your wife as "My sponsor"
All your family pictures are taken at Weigh-in
You fish Mclaurin Bay in early April
You sell a perfectly good Bass Boat and buy another one
Bass Pro sends you a get well soon card because you haven't been in for two weeks.   Art
You spend your entire spring flipping bitsy bugs for crappies and WGSF to scratch the itch
thats the best idea iv heard in years thanks
You post the same bass pic over and over again
you mistakenly refer to your wife as a lunker  you set a flippin jig in your own ear while practicing in the pool
your wife falls over and you ask  "did you see any fish while you were under"
...you can't catch any other species.
I found it funny   she didn't thought it better to ask before helping her back aboard   lmao
LMAO
You actually enjoy watching WFN!
You have this overwhelming urge to plug every brand name you have in your boat as you hoist the 10" beauty for the riffraff to drool over.
You know you're NOT addicted when you can't differentiate competitive tournament fishing from a relaxing, thrilling and incredibly rewarding sport called bass fishing.
Your boat has a Power Pole but you need Cialis.
When you spend every free moment working on your bass boat so that it can be ready for opener. (I'm holding a mirror here, Gent's)
The doctor holds up your newborn.      You blurt out it's a keeper!!
you use your ice gear and grubs to catch the chub you put in your back yard water feature   ?
You spent your honeymoon on Lake Okeechobee  You tie 50 pound test to the collar of your Pit Bull and play fetch.
You save a Bass and eat a chicken
